data.description: Welcome to 7743 W Shore Rd. Don't miss this one! Wonderfully kept Rancher in Pasadena with 4 Bedrooms and 3 full baths. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by the large living room with an abundance of natural light! Enter the kitchen to find plenty of cabinet space. Large back yard for your pets and entertainment. Fully finished basement with full bathroom, Bedroom and Living area. Master bedroom is nice size and has full bathroom. Owner has maintain the home very well. The laundry area is located on the lower level. The property features fresh paint. Conveniently located and in close proximity to plenty of shopping areas, schools, restaurants and major highways. Lots of off street parking and access to the back yard via gate
